class Environment:
	keep track of time
	run through control flow
	output performance object

class DataHandler:

class HistDataDotComHandler(DataHandler):


class OandaDataHandler(DataHandler):



class Optimize:
	given strategy and parameters to optimize, according to objectivefoo return set of optimal params

class Strategy:
	get_signals - any R in (-1,1) for each asset, along with order type optimized values


class Portfolio:
	keep track of positions, capital, capital_used, pnl, portfolio_value, start_capital, returns, start_date
	strategies, strategy_returns, interest_paid, commision_paid

	run through roundrobin all strategies in portfolio
	weight strategies signals based on some portfolio optimization techniques, calculate amount
	aggregate orders if possible
	submit orders

class Order:
	market, limit, stop, stoplimit, trailingstop, takeprofit

class Performance:
	strategies
	graph_returns
	graph_trades
	compare_strategies
	monte_carlo
	beta
	alpha
	other indicators

exceptionhandling close out all positions
daily report
